front.title: •••Scimitar Squadron TIE
front.gametext: Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. Power +3 during a Bombing Run battle. Cumulatively adds 1 to total weapon destiny of your other TIE/sa present firing Concussion Missiles.
front.lore: Bombers typically assigned to attack secondary targets and provide cover during bombing runs. Targeting systems calibrated to track fast-moving Rebel starfighters.
